---
// Hero.astro
---
<section id="inicio" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-petalo-dark">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-60">
    <img 
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526047932273-341f2a7631f9?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=2000" 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover" 
      alt="Hero Pétalo"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-petalo-dark/20 to-petalo-cream"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <span class="inline-block text-white text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-6 opacity-0 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      Florería Boutique & Diseño Floral
    </span>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-8xl text-white mb-8 leading-[1.1] opacity-0 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      Flores que cuentan <br/> <span class="italic font-normal text-petalo-rose">historias</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-white/80 text-lg md:text-xl font-light mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed opacity-0 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      Creamos experiencias visuales únicas con flores frescas seleccionadas a mano para transformar tus momentos especiales.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center opacity-0 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <a href="#catalogo" class="bg-white text-petalo-dark px-12 py-5 rounded-petalo font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest hover:bg-petalo-rose hover:text-white transition-all shadow-xl">
        Explorar Colección
      </a>
      <a href="#cotizar" class="border border-white/40 text-white backdrop-blur-md px-12 py-5 rounded-petalo font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:text-petalo-dark transition-all">
        Cotizar Evento
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .animate-fade-up {
    animation: fadeUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
  }
</style>